<plot>This made-for-tv documentary treats action and science fiction fans to a behind-the-scenes look at the making of Universal Soldier, about the result of a government project to create perfect fighting machines by reviving the dead bodies of soldiers killed in action. Includes interviews with stars Jean-Claude Van Damme and Dolph Lundgren, as well as the rest of the cast and crew of the film, who share their experiences from working on the project, and discuss the special efforts that went into bringing it to completion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?353779</url></doc>
